  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nWe're developing multi-client Ethereum deployer [kotal](https://kotal.co).\r\nAll Ethereum clients (geth, open ethereum, and besu) supports passing bootnodes to the node using `--bootnode` flag\r\nThere's no way to set bootnodes in Nethermind\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nAdd a new cli flag `--bootnodes` or `--discovery.bootnodes` that accepts a comma-separated node URLs\r\n\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nhttps://discord.com/channels/629004402170134531/629004402170134537/859495946761273345\r\n",
